flowchart TD
    A[Start: Client submits SQL statement]
    B[PostgreSQL receives SQL statement]
    A --> B

    C["Parse SQL statement (Lexer & Parser)"]
    B --> C

    D["Build Abstract Syntax Tree (AST)"]
    C --> D

    E[Semantic Analysis & Query Rewriting]
    D --> E

    F[Query Planning & Optimization]
    E --> F

    G[Generate Execution Plan]
    F --> G

    H[Execute Plan]
    G --> H

    I[Return results to client]
    H --> I
